(a) Sugars as defined in the Standard for sugars (CXS 212-1999);
(b) Salt (sodium chloride) as defined in the Standard for food-grade salt (CXS 150-1985);
(c) Edible fats and oils as defined in the Standard for named vegetable oils (CXS 210-1999) and in the Standard for named animal fats (CXS 211-1999);
